============================================================================================
POSITIVE CONTROL — calibration of W_IE by theta recovery
============================================================================================
  Sweep the inhibitory weight. Keep the range where the pipeline still
  recovers the 6 Hz theta that IS IN THE INPUT. This never looks at gamma.

     W_IE    rate_E    theta p   theta recovered in
  ----------------------------------------------------
     3 nS      9.5 Hz      0.000               100%
     6 nS      6.0 Hz      0.000               100% (adopted)
    10 nS      4.5 Hz      0.000               100%
    20 nS      3.2 Hz      0.000               100%

  Theta is recovered in 100% of seeds at 4 of 4 weights.
  => The control PASSES: the pipeline can see a rhythm that is known to
     be present, at every weight tested. It therefore has the power to
     say something about a rhythm that might not be.

     It does NOT discriminate among these weights, and no claim that it
     does should be made. W_IE = 6 nS is adopted because it yields a
     pyramidal rate of ~6 Hz, which is the physiological target. The
     choice is made on the rate column, not on the theta column.

